Mix @all-purpose flour{1.5%cups}, @salt{1/2%tsp}, and @baking powder{1.75%tsp} together, mix @sugar{3%Tbsp}, @eggs{2}, @melted butter{3%Tbsp}, and @milk{1%cup} together, add wet to dry and combine quickly.

Cook on a griddle.
